#math 
> [[4-11-22 Notes|4-11-22 Notes]]

We add a $w$ component to a point or a vector, like so:

$$
  Point = \left[\begin{matrix}P_{x}\\P_y\\\color{orange}1\end{matrix}\right]
  $$
$$
  \text{Vector}\ \ \vec{v} = \left[ \begin{matrix} v_{x} \\ v_{y} \\ \color{orange}0 \end{matrix} \right]
$$
This is [[New Extra Dimension Notation with Affine Transformations|New Extra Dimension Notation with Affine Transformations]]

---
$$
\begin{bmatrix}3\\4\\5\\1\end{bmatrix} \tilde{=}
\begin{bmatrix}6\\8\\10\\2\end{bmatrix}
$$
